| Time | Section | Duration |
|------|---------|----------|
| 0:00 | Architecture overview (use the diagram above) | 2 min |
| 2:00 | Dashboard tour — service discovery, fault catalog, health strip | 2 min |
| 4:00 | **Demo 3: Latency Injection** — the strongest demo, shows clear measurable impact | 5 min |
| 9:00 | Demo 2: Container Crash — quick, visual, shows cascade failure | 2 min |
| 11:00 | Demo 4: CPU Stress — resource exhaustion scenario | 2 min |
| 13:00 | Technical architecture walkthrough — pluggable registry, Docker SDK | 2 min |

> **Pro tip:** Start with the latency demo. It's the most impressive because it shows actual measured data with clear before/during/after comparison. Save the crash demo for second — it's visually dramatic but simpler to explain.
